2. **AI-Integrated Website Building.** You may not integrate, combine, or
   bundle the Licensed Work (or any derivative of it) with artificial
   intelligence, machine learning, large language models, or similar
   technologies to create, offer, or distribute an AI-powered website builder,
   code generation tool, or design-to-code service. This restriction applies
   whether such AI capabilities are built into the Licensed Work, layered on
