4. **Removal of Attribution.** Any derivative work, fork, or redistribution of
   the Licensed Work must prominently credit Absolute Studio and include a link
   to the original project repository (https://github.com/absolutejs/studio).

For clarity, the following uses are expressly permitted:

- Using Absolute Studio internally to build and develop your own applications,
